Package: auto-stretch
Version: 1.0.0
Section: science
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.9), python3-pip, python3-venv, siril
Maintainer: Auto Stretch Team <noreply@example.com>
Description: Advanced TIFF Image Stretching & Color Enhancement for Astronomy
 Auto Stretch is a Flask-based web application designed for processing
 astronomical TIFF images. It provides advanced stretching algorithms,
 color enhancement, and configurable parameters for astrophotography.
 .
 Features:
  - TIFF image upload and processing
  - Configurable gamma correction and tone curves
  - Color balance adjustments
  - Saturation boost controls
  - Optional Siril pre-processing integration
  - Web-based interface with astronomy theme
  - Runs as a systemd service on port 5000
Homepage: https://github.com/example/auto-stretch
